snippet.textDisplay: When we listen to Punjabi songs on Indian side they always have Lahore etc. in them and same goes for Pakistan Punjab side...like this song contains words like Ludhiana, raksha, Mitra, pyara, Chandigarh, Mansera etc...this made me think about how brutally India was partitioned and the animosity still runs deep but people still remember their past through these songs hopefully in a positive way.
